---
title: "US51 — Respond with expert advice"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>RequestDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SendDeliverable
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Deliverable · ServiceRequest
  A->>B: write advice / attach plan, tap SEND
  B->>C: send(requestId, deliverable)
  C->>E: insertDeliverable(requestId, content, attachments)
  alt delivered
    E-->>C: Deliverable (saved)
    C->>E: updateServiceRequestStatus(requestId, "completed")
    E-->>C: ServiceRequest (status = completed)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (sent)
    B-->>A: client sees it under purchases
  else send failed
    E-->>C: PostgrestException
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not send response. Try again."
  end
  note over E: human-expert advice — not AI.<br/>insertDeliverable / updateServiceRequestStatus via SupabaseGateway (RLS)
